title: Ep. - 259 - LANCE ARMSTRONG, ESPN 30 for 30 PSYCHIC MEDIUM THOMAS JOHN
description:
Juliet Macur, New York Times reporter and author of Cycle of Lies: The Fall of Lance Armstrong, reviews the new ESPN 30 for 30 two-part documentary Lance.

 

Psychic medium Thomas John talks about his new show CBS All Access’ new original series, The Thomas John Experience, which follows him as he journeys across America using his ability to connect unsuspecting everyday people with those on the other side.

 

 

Reality Life with Kate Casey
